  "rationale": "The Testimonials section is structured using a 1fr to 2fr CSS Grid ratio, prioritizing the quote content while maintaining a strong header presence on the left. Following Finsweet's 6-layer logic, the hierarchy ensures responsive stability. The quote uses heading-style-h5 for appropriate visual weight. Author details and navigation are unified in a space-between flex row to create a clean visual anchor at the bottom of the component. All interactive elements (arrows) and profile images follow exact rem dimensions (48px and 52px respectively) mapped from the design audit. The structure is compatible with Webflow's native Slider but uses custom div-based components for 1:1 visual fidelity as per MAS-V2-007."
}